<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/gallery/The-Great-Dragon-Spine.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="The-Great-Dragon-Spine.jpg" class="image" />
